  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK126">
<l>orumaiyu ḷāmaipō laintaṭakka lāṟṟi</l>
<l>ṉeḻumaiyu mēmāp puṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If in one birth one is able, like the tortoise, to restrain the five,</l>
<l>it gives protection through the seven.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
